Name: Wisp Stalks
Description: Found near dead marshes, these stalks seem to crackle with a flickering light. Ensure proper insulation precautions are taken, never handle directly.
Types: Potion, Bomb
Potion: Melee attacks made with a metallic weapon deal an extra RANDOM3DICE lightning damage on a hit while under the effects of this potion.
Potion: Cures Paralyzed status.
Bomb: Creatures within 5 feet of the radius are subjected to the bomb's effect as if they were within the affected area. 
